1. *Klarka* je najmlađa članica naše ekipe. (Clark is the youngest member of our team.)
2. *Klark* je već tri godine u braku. (Clark has been married for three years.)
3. Da li ste čuli za *Klarka* Kent? (Have you heard of Clark Kent?)
4. Moja sestra je *Klarkov* veliki fan. (My sister is a big fan of Clark.)
5. *Klarkov* posao je vrlo zahtevan. (Clark's job is very demanding.)
6. *Klark* se bavi pisanjem pesama. (Clark is involved in songwriting.)
7. Na kraju filma, *Klark* se oprostio od publike. (At the end of the movie, Clark said goodbye to the audience.)
8. *Klarka* je bila iznenađena kada je dobila poziv za intervju. (Clark was surprised when she received an invitation for an interview.)
9. *Klarka* je uspešna preduzetnica. (Clark is a successful entrepreneur.)
10. *Klarku* smo poslali mejl sa zahtevom za informacijama. (We sent Clark an email requesting information.)